	<summary>Integration of Cristal in Nextcloud</summary>
	<description><![CDATA[The Cristal app is a wiki application for [Nextcloud](https://www.nextcloud.com/). It provides usual wiki features such as page hierarchy, linking pages, a rich editor, or attachments.

    The wiki content is persisted in the user's files in Markdown.

		This is an integration of the [Cristal UI](https://cristal.xwiki.org) in Nextcloud, which is also usable in other contexts.]]></description>
